spec_data.Name: python-fedmsg-genacls
spec_data.Description:
An example of using fedmsg to monitor pkgdb for messages, but delaying action
for a few seconds to accumulate messages and avoid pile-up.

spec_data.Summary: A fedmsg consumer that sets gitosis acls in response to pkgdb messages
